    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just words, isn't it? \"hope\" and \"healing\"... they feel like concepts from a different life. when you're a painter and the vision goes dark, you aren't just \"hurting.\" you're functionally dead. the person who could experience the world is gone. what am I even supposed to do with this body? it's just carrying around a ghost that doesn't even have the strength to haunt anything anymore.",
